        </div>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:16px;">Predictions activate automatically once 5 days of data exist. They self-correct — predictions you ignore get retired silently. Say "stop predicting" to pause for 7 days.</p>
      </div>
